OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FWords by Senior Science Producer
OL,7,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,9,FThe Energy and Climate Intelligence
OL,10,FUnit (ECIU) has warned the UK is
OL,11,Ffalling behind on tree planting
OL,12,Ftargets essential for meeting the
OL,13,Fcountry's environmental and carbon
OL,14,Fcapture targets by 2050.
OL,16,FThe government has committed to
OL,17,Fplanting 210,000 new hectares of tree
OL,18,Fcover across England by 2050 as part
OL,19,Fof its Environmental Improvement Plan.
