OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FThe trees will have a key role in
OL,7,Fremoving carbon from the atmosphere,
OL,8,Fimproving flood defences and helping
OL,9,Fto grow wildlife habitats.
OL,11,FHowever, analysis by the ECIU has
OL,12,Ffound that more than 70% of carbon
OL,13,Fremoval from new trees will come from
OL,14,Fthose planted within the next five
OL,15,Fyears, warning that the UK is
OL,16,Fcurrently behind on its tree planting
OL,17,Ftargets within this time frame.
