OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FThis is because trees need time to
OL,7,Fmature and establish themselves to be
OL,8,Feffective carbon removers. It means
OL,9,Fthose trees planted by 2030 will be
OL,10,Fthe most crucial in helping to achieve
OL,11,Fthe government's carbon removal goals.
OL,13,FThe ECIU analysis warns that the
OL,14,Fgovernment cannot afford to fall
OL,15,Fbehind on these planting targets if it
OL,16,Fhopes to still meet the goals set for
OL,17,F2050.
