OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FThe analysis found that higher
OL,7,Fplanting rates in the future cannot
OL,8,Fcompensate for missed planting now due
OL,9,Fto the time lag before trees mature
OL,10,Fenough to deliver maximum benefits for
OL,11,Fcarbon removal, biodiversity and flood
OL,12,Frisk prevention.
OL,14,FMature trees are also beneficial in
OL,15,Fprotecting homes against the risk of
OL,16,Fflooding by slowing the flow of water
OL,17,Fduring downpours, something that
OL,18,Fjuvenile trees are not as effective at.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
