OL,3,CUK risks missing climate targets
OL,4,Cwithout rapid tree planting
OL,6,FClimate change projections show 1.7
OL,7,Fmillion more homes will be at risk of
OL,8,Fflooding by 2050.
OL,10,FTom Cantillon, a senior analyst at the
OL,11,FECIU said: "Trees sucking carbon out
OL,12,Fof the atmosphere are critical to the
OL,13,FUK reaching net zero - the only way
OL,14,Fthe world can stop climate change and
OL,15,Fbring our climate back into balance.
